    "Second, Internet retrieval can be utilized to reduce the overhead of the retriever, but attention needs to be paid to the data relevance mentioned earlier.",
    "Finally, In-context learning can be employed to reduce the overhead associated with improving LMs, e.g., ICRALM (Ram et al., 2023).",
    "In the contemporary era, the application of LLM has been expanded to encompass a multitude of domains, whereas the application direction of RALM remains relatively limited.",
    "To address this limi-tation, researchers must not only consider the existing application areas of LLM but also leverage the distinctive strengths of RALM, which excels in addressing problems closely related to knowledge and experience.",
